<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.2.3">
<l>mallōṭukañca ṉumtuñcaveṉṟa maṇivaṇṇaṉ</l>
<l>allimalarttaṇ ṭuḻāyniṉainti runtēṉaiyē</l>
<l>elliyiṉmārutam vantaṭumatu vaṉṟiyum</l>
<l>kollaivallēṟ ṟiṉmaṇiyuṅkō yiṉmaiceyyumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The wind comes in the night and destroys me who is thinking</l>
<l>Of the cool tulasī, petals unfurling, of the jewel-hued one</l>
<l>Who conquered Kamsa and the wrestlers, so they perished;</l>
<l rend="indent">besides that,</l>
<l>Even the bells on the strong bulls in the field do [me] an injustice.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
